English Translation

When I turn the lights on in my room
Will someone hug the lonely me?
The ramen that I cook so badly
Who will eat it with me now?
You were the type who hugged me
And said I wasn’t a quiet and cold person
When my hands were so cold
That you didn’t let go all night
I miss it, I feel so frustrated today

Sometimes you think of me and smile
Our conversations captured in confidence
Today I would hide buried in the bed
Eh-eh without you at night I feel lonely

Pretending to be strong makes me sick everyday
Like a love song made for you
Scent in my bed is only you
The trace I cant clean Just cant do it
Tonight I want to go to you
In just a dream

Saying that I’ll forget you is so easy
I hate myself for trying to forget you
Saying that I’ll forget you is so easy
I hate myself so much for trying to forget you BABE

Why do I compare you to the girls who like me
No matter how shine they are there is no sympathetic I do not have any inspiration either they love or not

I cannot avoid cases
While my soul lost in love
My bodies will torn in pieces
I'd rather be lonely
I erase myself so no one remembers me
I'm sorry I cannot anymore
This is what you said to me
But I love you
This is the most I regret saying

